>\n其他人掩護<br />\n一但成功 拋走裝備入人群 推走隻狗<br />\n<br />\n有錯求指點"},{"pid":"4f1cbdd05093a3378aca0ffda83816ec5390af01","tid":1215458,"uid":235796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"Push,btw唔建議同警犬玩埋身始終捉得實你的話會攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a231643a211922e8e8c846ea62783f01b374ed1","tid":1215458,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"白版做通訊同指示"},{"pid":"45f9935ac799110dc6cf9c72241f3a851f2ed04f","tid":1215458,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1af42eadc5c26939fd0575416c7aac314ede88","tid":1215458,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a373de911e9fd32d71bb7de2ea903b53521c8fa5","tid":1215458,"uid":139860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:24:10.000Z","msg":"Push 尋日發夢真係好混亂 講真又唔係有牌黑社會 平時唔似佢哋有演習定點 出到淆就一定會 但係一亂就仲淆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"要搵翻個秩序，但好有難度，大家有咩諗法？"},{"pid":"2e73a6a2f0134240d97a2ac867f47d5dc09251a8","tid":1215458,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5a7beecaa2fb79c5144a06b700841a8a37a73bd","tid":1215458,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"walkie成本較高 <br />\n旗就平同可以俾所有人睇到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"除咗walkie，仲有咩方法俾前線可以溝通？<br />\n始終旗可以傳達嘅比較有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6134ee54cebd7ca4ce4b91e17419eeaf236fa2","tid":1215458,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"809e9c8598b8ee7cff8a3d63bf87ad19fe18afe8","tid":1215458,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見佢地訂左好多瑜伽墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re